    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AD1S/KH9\nWake Islang\nWESI/KH9\nCraig",
      "1991 CQWW Wake Island DXpedition\nWE5I/KH9\nWAKE ISLAND - A possession of the U.S. is a typical Pacific\ncoral atoll consisting of three islands - Wake Island, Wilkes\nAD1S/KH9\nIsland, and Peale Island connected by a bridge and a causeway.\nTotal landmass is about 2.5 square miles built up on a underwater\nSpecial Thanks To:\nvolcano.\nMajor Michael Koch, USAF\nJohn Beardshear, KB5LRO\nSSgt John Lang, USAF\nDet 4 15th Air Base Wing\nUSAF Military Airlift Command\nTom Russell, AH9AC\nKwajalein Amateur Radio Club\nKen Wells, V73CT\nQSL to: OKDXA\nBox 88\nWellston, OK 74881\nOK\nDX\nOKlahoma DX\nAssociation\nSupport Group:\nWR5G, KG5MA, N5QKK, N5PVM, KA5PSF, WN5J,\nN5DLM, N5QOR, N5MIH, W5CCP AND MARCIA\nConfirming QSO with: AC2P\n27-Oct-91 2208 UTC 10 2XSSB\n59\nOklahoma\nComm\nCenter\nCo World Wide - Thanks SL"
